* get_mac_address_table
* get_ntp_peers
* get_ntp_servers
* get_ntp_stats
* get_snmp_information
* [...]

## How to release

```
git tag v0.3.2 <commit hash>
git push --tags
```

Actions should take care of the rest and cut a release and push it to pypi


